Fix for hiding help icon pushed to develop at http://git.io/iiBYyg

Note that the help icon was displaying since the landing page styles are pulled in for the user detail page (as it needs to in order to display the tile view for the groups), so the workaround for any page that pulls in landing page styles and isn't a landing page is to add the following CSS to hide the help icon.

#breadcrumbs .icon-block \{ display: none; \}
